'''''Rent a Friend''''' (2000) is a film directed by [[Eddy Terstall]]. The film was produced by  Jordaan Film, BNN TV.<ref name=NYT>{{cite web|title=Rent a Friend|url=http://www.nytimes.com/movies/movie/187065/Rent-a-Friend/overview|publisher=NYT|accessdate=7 May 2015}}</ref><ref name=Letterboxd>{{cite web|title=Rent a Friend|url=http://letterboxd.com/film/rent-a-friend/|publisher=Letterboxd|accessdate=7 May 2015}}</ref>

== Plot ==
Arthur is a talented artist. He does not care to be rich or famous and gives full attention to his artworks and creation. Moniek, his girlfriend is a successful writer. Alfred's lack of ambition and negligence towards money and material life irritates Arthur.<ref name="Movie Meter">{{cite web|title=Rent-a-Friend|url=http://www.moviemeter.nl/film/1390|publisher=Movie Meter|accessdate=7 May 2015}}</ref><ref name=Film1>{{cite web|title=Rent A Friend (2000)|url=http://www.film1.nl/films/130-Rent-A-Friend.html|publisher=Film1|accessdate=7 May 2015}}</ref>

== Cast ==
* Marc Van Uchelen as Arthur 
* Rifka Lodeizen as Moniek 
* Nadja Hupscher as Fran<U+00E7>oise 
* Huub Stapel as Mr. Black Pudding 
* Victor L<U+00F6>w as Mr. German Blood 
* Peer Mascini as Smulders 

